property.type_description: Automatically generated from the team list
property.name: Owner

property_definition.name: Accepted On
property_definition.description: Date that the story was accepted by the customer

property_definition.name: Defect Reported On
property_definition.description: Date that a defect was discovered

property_definition.name: Defect Time-To-Life
property_definition.description: Number of days elapsed between reporting a defect and it being fixed.

property_definition.name: Development Completed On
property_definition.description: Date that development was completed for the story

property_definition.name: Number of Iterations Remaining
property_definition.formula: (('Total Planning Estimate' - 'Total Points Accepted') / (('Total Points Accepted' / 'Total Closed Iterations')))

property_definition.name: Owner
property_definition.description: Individual signed up to work on a card
property_definition.property_values_description: Automatically generated from the team list

property_definition.name: Planning Estimate
property_definition.description: Estimate made for a story in the early phases of the project for planning purposes.

property_definition.name: Priority
property_definition.description: Level of criticality assigned to a card. Common values include (critical, essential, non-essential)

property_definition.name: Reported By
property_definition.property_values_description: Automatically generated from the team list

property_definition.name: Risk Impact
property_definition.description: Monetary impact of the risk occuring

property_definition.name: Story Status
property_definition.description: The status of the story or task. Stories and tasks share the same lifecycle (state values and state transitions).

property_definition.name: Story Time-To-Life
property_definition.description: Number of days elapsed between moving a story into scope and it being accepted by the customer.
